ARTICLE.TITLE: Former President Lee Teng-hui remembered in private funeral

og.title: Former President Lee Teng-hui remembered in private funeral - Focus Taiwan
og.description: Taipei, Aug. 14 (CNA) A private funeral was held early Friday in Taipei for former President Lee Teng-hui (李登輝), a central figure in Taiwan's transition to democracy who died July 30 at the age of 97.
